flowchart TD
    A[XRPL API Call] --> B{Success?}
    B -->|Yes| C[Validate Response]
    C --> D[Save CSV Output]
    D --> E[AI or Fallback Summary]
    E --> F[Mark Completed]

    B -->|Timeout| G[Retry with Backoff]
    G --> A

    B -->|Rate Limit| H[Wait Longer]
    H --> A

    B -->|Invalid Response| I[Save to Dead Letter]
    E -->|OpenAI Error| J[Create Fallback Summary]
    J --> K[Log Error to Dead Letter]
    J --> F
